%20across%20nearby%20landscapes%20and%20ignited%20a%20small%20fire.%20Metal%20sheets%20and%20insulation%20were%20also%20found%20among%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20environmental%20practices%20have%20caused%20friction%20with%20government%20agencies%20like%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20and%20the%20US%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20defended%20SpaceX%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBlowing%20debris%20into%20state%20parks%20or%20national%20land%20is%20not%20what%20we%20prescribed%2C%20but%20the%20bottom%20line%20is%20no%20one%20got%20hurt%2C%20no%20one%20got%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20certainly%20don't%20want%20people%20to%20feel%20like%20they're%20bulldozed.%20But%20it's%20a%20really%20important%20operation%20that%20SpaceX%20is%20conducting%20down%20there.%20It%20is%20really%20important%20to%20our%20civilian%20space%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Henry%2C%20a%20former%20SpaceX%20advisor%20on%20Pentagon%20launch%20programs%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20SpaceX%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20criticisms%20surrounding%20its%20environmental%20practices%20and%20plans%20to%20address%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20reported%20that%20SpaceX%20hired%20a%20consultant%20to%20track%20bird%20patterns%2C%20and%20its%20researchers%20%26quot%3Bfound%20little%20to%20no%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20changes%20to%20the%20local%20bird%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SpaceX%20Starship%20spacecraft%20at%20Starbase%20in%20Boca%20Chica%2C%20Texas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668b051b1aace5b3ada4e216%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpaceX's%20Starship%20spacecraft%20at%20Starbase%20in%20Boca%20Chica%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ECHANDAN%20KHANNA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20environmental%20officials%20have%20more%20grievances%20with%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20reported%20that%20SpaceX%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bexploited%20the%20limitations%20and%20competing%20missions%20of%20the%20various%20agencies%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20impose%20unfavorable%20regulations.%20The%20National%20Park%20Service%20and%20US%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20offices%2C%20which%20oversee%20natural%20and%20other%20resources%2C%20have%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%26quot%3B%20lost%20to%20larger%20agencies%20like%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20also%20reported%20that%20Musk%20has%20expanded%20SpaceX's%20operations%20more%20than%20he%20initially%20promised%20officials.%20A%20former%20National%20Park%20Service%20official%2C%20Mark%20Spier%2C%20said%20SpaceX%20%26quot%3Bmisled%26quot%3B%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20kept%20saying%2C%20'No%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C'%20and%20then%20they%20came%20back%20and%20said%2C%20'Yes%2C%20we%20are%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20being%20misled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20around%20SpaceX%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20local%20environments%20has%20continued%20to%20gain%20traction.%20NASA%20confirmed%20in%20June%20that%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20debris%20the%20size%20of%20a%20car%20hood%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-nasa-need-better-space-debris-models-reduce-impact-risk-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpaceX's%20Dragon%20Capsule%3C%2Fa%3E%20crashed%20in%20North%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20from%20SpaceX%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20and%20the%20US%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20req