%20being%20hospitalised.%20The%20yatra%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20religious%20gatherings%2C%20witnessed%20an%20even%20higher%20turnout%20this%20year%20because%20it%20is%20being%20held%20over%20two%20days%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20stressed%20that%20the%20death%20was%20due%20to%20suffocation%20and%20there%20was%20no%20stampede-like%20situation%20despite%20lakhs%20of%20people%20gathering%20to%20witness%20-%20and%20participate%20in%20-%20the%20chariots%20of%20Lord%20Jagannath%2C%20Devi%20Subhadra%20and%20Lord%20Balabhadra%20being%20taken%20to%20visit%20their%20maternal%20aunt%2C%20Goddess%20Gundicha%20Devi%2C%20at%20her%20temple%20around%202.5%20km%20away%2C%20and%20then%20brought%20back.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20death%20of%20the%20man%20was%20caused%20by%20heat%20and%20humidity%20coupled%20with%20the%20rush.%20Adequate%20arrangements%20had%20been%20made%20and%20ambulances%20were%20deployed%20to%20attend%20to%20such%20situations%2C%20they%20emphasised.%20Despite%20water%20being%20sprinkled%20on%20the%20devotees%20to%20keep%20them%20cool%2C%20several%20people%20could%20be%20seen%20carried%20out%20on%20stretchers%20and%20taken%20away%20in%20ambulances%20after%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Odisha%20and%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MLA%2C%20also%20attended%20the%20yatra%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pulling%20of%20the%20chariots%20began%20around%205.20%20pm%20after%20Puri%20Shankaracharya%20Swami%20Nischalanada%20Saraswati%20went%20to%20the%20chariots%20of%20Lord%20Jagannath%2C%20Lord%20Balabhadra%20and%20Devi%20Subhadra%20with%20his%20disciples%20and%20Puri's%20titular%20king%20completed%20the%20'Chhera%20Pahanra'%20(chariot%20sweeping)%20ritual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%2C%20Odisha%20Governor%20Raghubar%20Das%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Charan%20Majhi%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20symbolically%20started%20the%20mammoth%20exercise%20by%20pulling%20the%20ropes%20attached%20to%20the%20main%20chariot%20of%20Lord%20Jagannath.%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20also%20paid%20obeisance%20to%20the%20deities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETight%20security%20arrangements%20were%20in%20place%2C%20with%20the%20deployment%20of%20180%20platoons%20(each%2030-strong)%20of%20security%20personnel%2C%20Puri%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Pinak%20Mishra%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20Drones%20were%20also%20deployed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20cameras%20with%20AI%20technology%20were%20installed%20at%20Badadanda%2C%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20festival%2C%20and%20other%20strategic%20locations%20in%20the%20town%2C%20said%20ADG%20(law%20and%20order)%20Sanjay%20Kumar.%20As%20many%20as%2046%20fire%20tenders%20were%20also%20in%20place%20and%20DG%2C%20fire%20service%2C%20Sudhanshu%20Sarangi%20said%20water%20was%20sprinkled%20on%20the%20crowd%20to%20keep%20them%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720375500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ffpbamchg_puri-rath-yatra-crowd_625x300_07_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuri-rath-yatra-rath-yatra-man-dies-of-suffocation-as-lakhs-gather-for-puri-rath-yatra-6055402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20massive%20crowd%20at%20the%20Puri%20Rath%20Yatra%20has%20led%20to%20one%20person%20dying%20of%20suffocation%20and%20several%20others%20being%20hospitalised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuri-rath-yatra-rath-yatra-man-dies-of-suffocation-as-lakhs-gather-for-puri-rath-yatra-6055402%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpuri-rath-yatra-rath-yatra-man-dies-of-suffocation-as-