20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20Russia%20since%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20will%20review%20the%20entire%20range%20of%20multifaceted%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20exchange%20views%20on%20contemporary%20regional%20and%20global%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%20while%20announcing%20the%20high-level%20visit%20starting%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20Moscow%20will%20be%20extensive%20and%20the%20two%20leaders%20will%20be%20able%20to%20have%20informal%20talks%2C%20Kremlin%20Spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Russia's%20state-run%20VGTRK%20television%20channel%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CObviously%2C%20the%20agenda%20will%20be%20extensive%2C%20if%20not%20to%20say%20overbusy.%20It%20will%20be%20an%20official%20visit%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20the%20heads%20will%20be%20able%20to%20talk%20in%20an%20informal%20way%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Peskov%20said%20that%20Russian-Indian%20relations%20are%20at%20the%20level%20of%20strategic%20partnership.%20He%20said%20that%20there%20would%20be%20both%20one-on-one%20talks%20in%20the%20Kremlin%20and%20those%20involving%20delegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20expecting%20a%20very%20important%20and%20full-fledged%20visit%2C%20which%20is%20so%20crucial%20for%20Russian-Indian%20relations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20official%20Tass%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Peskov%20also%20emphasised%20that%20the%20West%20is%20closely%20and%20jealously%20watching%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20upcoming%20visit%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20jealous%20%E2%80%94%20that%20means%20they%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20it.%20Their%20close%20monitoring%20means%20they%20attach%20great%20importance%20to%20it.%20And%20they%20are%20not%20mistaken%2C%20there%20is%20something%20to%20attach%20great%20importance%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Peskov%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20about%20the%20jealous%20attitude%20of%20Western%20politicians%20towards%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Russia%2C%20the%20Tass%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20held%20several%20telephonic%20conversations%20with%20Mr%20Putin%20and%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%2C%20stressing%20the%20importance%20of%20ending%20the%20war%20that%20has%20impacted%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reflection%20of%20its%20strong%20friendship%20with%20Russia%2C%20India%20has%20not%20yet%20condemned%20Moscow's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20it%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20the%20conflict%20must%20be%20resolved%20through%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20import%20of%20discounted%20Russian%20crude%20oil%20has%20also%20gone%20up%20significantly%20notwithstanding%20the%20G7%20price%20cap%20and%20increasing%20disquiet%20over%20the%20procurement%20in%20many%20Western%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20Russia%20in%20nearly%20five%20years.%20His%20last%20visit%20to%20Russia%20was%20in%202019%20when%20he%20attended%20an%20economic%20conclave%20in%20the%20Far%20East%20city%20of%20Vladivostok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20summit%20between%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20and%20the%20president%20of%20Russia%20is%20the%20highest%20institutional%20dialogue%20mechanism%20in%20the%20strategic%20partnership%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%2021%20annual%20summits%20have%20taken%20place%20alternately%20in%20India%20and%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20annual%20summit%20was%20held%20on%20December%206%2C%202021%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20when%20Mr%20Putin%20visited%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720368180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fu1sjd15_modi-putin-ani-650_650x400_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-russia-visit-pm-modi-russia-west-watching-with-jealousy-kremlin-on-pm-modis-russia-visit-6054773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20expecting%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20important%20and%20full-fledged%20visit%26quot%3B%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20Moscow%20for%20summit-level%20talks%20with%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20with%20the%20Kremlin%20saying%20the%20West%20was%20watching%20the%20trip%20with%20%26quot%3Bjealousy%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-russia-visit-pm-modi-russia-west-watching-with-jealousy-kremlin-on-pm-modis-russia-visit-6054773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-russia-visit-pm-modi-russia-west-watching-with-jealousy-kremlin-on-pm-modis-russia-visit-6054773%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-russia-visit-pm-modi-russia-west-watching-with-jealousy-kremlin-on-pm-modis-russia-visit-6054773%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sena%20Leader%20Arrested%2C%20Son%20On%20The%20Run%20In%20Mumbai%20BMW%20Hit-And-Run%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20speeding%20BMW%20that%20hit%20a%20scooter%20in%20Mumbai's%20Worli%20this%20morning%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20woman's%20death%2C%20was%20being%20driven%20by%20the%2024-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20police%20have%20said.%20The%20police%20also%C2%A0suspect%20that%20Mihir%20Shah%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run%2C%20was%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%C2%A0His%20blood%20test%20report%20is%20awaited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Rajesh%20Shah%2C%20deputy%20leader%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Palghar%20district.%20The%20politician%20and%20his%20driver%2C%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Bijawat%2C%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20evening%20for%20not%20cooperating%20with%20the%20police%2C%20among%20other%20charges%2C%20and%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20new%20criminal%20code%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%2C%20rash%20driving%20and%20destruction%20of%20evidence%2C%20among%20others.%20Provisions%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%20have%20also%20been%20invoked.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20is%20registered%20in%20Mihir%20Shah's%20name.%C2%A0At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20police%20said%2C%20the%20Sena%20leader's%20son%20and%20their%20driver%20were%20in%20the%20luxury%20car.%C2%A0According%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20drank%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20Juhu%20last%20night.%20On%20his%20way%20home%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20driver%20to%20take%20him%20for%20a%20long%20drive.%20The%20car%20came%20to%20Worli%20and%20then%20Mihir%20insisted%20that%20he%20would%20drive.%20Soon%20after%20he%20took%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20speeding%20BMW%20hit%20a%20scooter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20scooter%20were%20Kaveri%20Nakva%20and%20her%20husband%20Pradik%20Nakva%2C%20residents%20of%20Worli's%20Koliwada%20area.%20The%20fish-seller%20couple%20went%20to%20Sassoon%20Dock%20daily%20to%20fetch%20fish.%20They%20were%20on%20their%20way%20back%2C%20when%20the%20BMW%20crashed%20into%20their%20two-wheeler.%20The%20two%20were%20thrown%20into%20the%20air%20and%20crashed%20on%20the%20bonnet%20of%20the%20SUV.%20As%20the%20car%20kept%20speeding%2C%20Kaveri%20Nakva%20was%20run%20over.%20The%20car%20fled%20the%20spot%20and%20the%20woman%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20declared%20dead.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Pradik%2C%20suffered%20minor%20injuries.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20have%20said%C2%A0Mihir%20called%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20about%20the%20crash.%20His%20phone%20has%20been%20off%20since%20then.%20Four%20police%20teams%20are%20looking%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police's%20investigation%20has%20also%20revealed%20attempts%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20The%20car's%20windshield%20has%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20sticker%2C%20which%20has%20been%20scratched%2C%20apparently%20to%20conceal%20the%20vehicle's%20link%20with%20the%20Sena%20leader.%20One%20of%20the%20car's%20number%20plates%20was%20also%20removed%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20but%20police%20scanned%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20area%20to%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Sena%20Leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20termed%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20and%20assured%20action.%20%26quot%3BLaw%20will%20take%20its%20own%20course%2C%20everyone%20is%20equal%20before%20law.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20police%20and%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20similar%20case%20of%20drink-driving%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20dead%20in%20Pune.%20The%20minor%20accused%20in%20the%20Pune%20crash%20was%20speeding%20a%20Porsche%20car%20after%20a%20round%20of%20drinking.%20The%20teen's%20father%2C%20a%20prominent%20realtor%2C%20his%20mother%20and%20his%20grandfather%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%20for%20allegedly%20attempting%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720367400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.