inal%20Law%20Over%20Comment%20On%20X%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20case%20related%20to%20outraging%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20for%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20chief%20Rekha%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Ms%20Sharma%2C%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20was%20registered%20by%20the%20special%20cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Sunday%20under%20Section%2079%20(word%2C%20gesture%20or%20act%20intended%20to%20insult%20modesty%20of%20woman)%20of%20the%20new%20criminal%20code%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20has%20replaced%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sharma%20has%20also%20written%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20requested%20him%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20from%20West%20Bengal's%20Krishnanagar%2C%20who%20was%20disqualified%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20year%20after%20the%20'cash-for-query'%20row%20and%20was%20re-elected%20this%20year%2C%20had%20made%20a%20remark%20on%20Thursday%20in%20reaction%20to%20videos%20of%20the%20women's%20commission%20chief%20meeting%20women%20injured%20in%20the%20Hathras%20stampede%20in%20which%20121%20people%20were%20killed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20showed%20someone%20holding%20up%20an%20umbrella%20for%20Ms%20Sharma%20and%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bpajamas%26quot%3B%20reference%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20which%20had%20sparked%20a%20controversy.%C2%A0She%20later%20deleted%20the%20post%20and%20the%20police%20have%20sought%20details%20about%20it%20from%20the%20social%20media%20giant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Take%20Immediate%20Action'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(NCW)%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20remark%20on%20Friday%20and%20sought%20a%20case%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20but%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20had%20remained%20combative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20post%20by%20the%20NCW%20on%20X%20she%20had%20tagged%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20take%20immediate%20action%20and%20arrest%20her%2C%20even%20telling%20them%20that%20she%20was%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Nadia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20on%20%40DelhiPolice%20%C2%A0please%20take%20action%20immediately%20on%20these%20suo%20moto%20orders.%20Am%20in%20Nadia%20in%20case%20you%20need%20me%20in%20the%20next%203%20days%20to%20make%20a%20quick%20arrest%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Moitra%20wrote%2C%20appending%20an%20%26quot%3BI%20Can%20Hold%20My%20Own%20Umbrella%26quot%3B%20dig%20against%20Ms%20Sharma%20at%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosting%20earlier%20tweets%20by%20Ms%20Sharma%20in%20which%20the%20NCW%20chief%20appeared%20to%20call%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20former%20Congress%20President%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20dumb%20and%20made%20a%20joke%20against%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bsuhaag%20raat%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20reference%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20also%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20take%20action%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bserial%20offender%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20leader%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20December%20last%20year%20based%20on%20an%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20on%20the%20alleged%20'cash-for-query'%20charges%20against%20her.%20She%20was%20accused%20of%20taking%20bribes%2C%20including%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%20cash%20and%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20gifts%26quot%3B%2C%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament%20that%20were%20critical%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20Agencies%20are%20also%20investigating%20that%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720362060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fk5p1ma3s_mah