tle%22%3A%22Centre%20Acts%20Against%202%20Kolkata%20Senior%20Cops%20For%20%26quot%3BTarnishing%26quot%3B%20Governor's%20Office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20initiated%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20Vineet%20Goyal%20and%20a%20DCP%20for%20allegedly%20maligning%20the%20office%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20by%20promoting%20and%20spreading%20canards%2C%20a%20central%20government%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20ministry%20action%20came%20after%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20submitted%20a%20report%20to%20it%20regarding%20Vineet%20Goyal%20and%20Kolkata%20Police%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20(DCP)%20Central%20Indira%20Mukherjee%2C%20alleging%20that%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bfunctioning%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20is%20completely%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20public%20servant%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECV%20Ananda%20Bose's%20report%2C%20submitted%20to%20the%20Home%20Minister%20in%20late%20June%2C%20highlighted%20issues%20such%20as%20Kolkata%20Police%20officers%20preventing%20victims%20of%20post-poll%20violence%20from%20meeting%20the%20Governor%20despite%20his%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20initiated%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20the%20IPS%20officers%20based%20on%20a%20detailed%20report%20by%20Mr%20Bose%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20told%20PTI.%20Copies%20of%20the%20letter%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20state%20government%20on%20July%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor%20also%20accused%20other%20police%20officers%2C%20posted%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20of%20promoting%20and%20encouraging%20concocted%20allegations%20by%20a%20woman%20employee%20during%20April-May%202024%2C%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20IPS%20officers%20through%20their%20acts%20have%20not%20only%20tarnished%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Governor%20but%20also%20functioned%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20is%20completely%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20public%20servant.%20They%20have%20conveniently%20chosen%20to%20ignore%20the%20Conduct%20Rules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20report%2C%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20mentioned%20Kolkata%20Police's%20alleged%20new%20practice%20of%20issuing%20identity%20cards%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan%20staff%20and%20frisking%20them%20upon%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20despite%20objections%20from%20the%20Governor's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreventing%20a%20delegation%20of%20victims%20of%20violence%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20from%20meeting%20Mr%20Bose%20and%20subsequently%20detaining%20them%20is%20an%20affront%20to%20the%20Constitutional%20authority%20of%20the%20Governor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20troubling%20that%20the%20victims%20had%20to%20move%20court%20to%20meet%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20Police's%20%26quot%3Btotal%20silence%26quot%3B%20on%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose's%20June%2013%20directive%20to%20remove%20the%20police%20contingent%20from%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20seen%20as%20defying%20orders%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20mid-June%2C%20Kolkata%20Police%20posted%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20unilaterally%20set%20up%20a%20'security%20mechanism'%20without%20the%20Governor's%20knowledge%20and%20consent%2C%20effectively%20placing%20the%20entire%20establishment%20under%20'arrest'%20and%20'watch'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECV%20Ananda%20Bose's%20report%20also%20mentioned%20that%20a%20preliminary%20internal%20inquiry%20found%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20molestation%20against%20him%20by%20a%20former%20Raj%20Bhavan%20employee%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpre-written%20script.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BKolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20and%20Indira%20Mukherjee%20formed%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20with%20unusual%20speed%20and%20continued%20media%20briefings%20to%20create%20a%20false%20impression%20that%20the%20Governor%20could%20face%20criminal%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20alleged%20that%20Vineet%20Goyal%20and%20Mukherjee%20were%20instrumental%20in%20promoting%20another%20'complaint'%20from%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20reported%20that%20Kolkata%20Police%20registered%20a%20'zero%20FIR'%20at%20a%20local%20police%20station%20and%20transferred%20the%20case%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20On%20June%2017%2C%202024%2C%20the%20alleged%20complainant%20publicly%20said%20she%20had%20nothing%20against%20the%20Governor%20and%20wanted%20to%20withdraw%20it.%20However%2C%20Kolkata%20Police%20did%20not%20allow%20her%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECV%20Ananda%20Bose%20had%20written%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20requesting%20action%20against%20Vineet%20Goyal%20and%20Indira%20Mukherjee%2C%20but%20no%20steps%20were%20taken%2C%20nor%20was%20there%20any%20communication%20from%20her%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECV%20Ananda%20Bose%20also%20referred%20to%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20Siliguri%20to%20meet%20victims%20of%20Chopra%20violence%2C%20questioning%20the%20conduct%20of%20some%20officials%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20conduct%20is%20not%20per%20the%20All%20India%20Services%20rules%20and%20protocol%20manuals.%20The%20state%20government%20was%20duly%20informed.%20However%2C%20in%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20protocol%2C%20the%20Darjeeling%20DM%20and%20Siliguri%20Police%20Commissioner%20did%20not%20call%20on%20the%20Governor.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20was%20not%20a%20one-off%20incident.%20There%20have%20been%20several%20similar%20cases%20of%20such%20lapses%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20Vineet%20