20to%20hide%20my%20arms%2C%20but%20to%20match%20the%20season.%20I%20chose%20to%20be%20bold%20and%20stay%20true%20to%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b14eaa4-02ec-485e-8956-0a8f7dd9e32e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20all%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20though%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20photos%20were%20going%20to%20look%20awful.%20We%20got%20the%20photos%20back%20online%20first.%20I%20was%20too%20nervous%20to%20look%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20wait%20until%20we%20received%20the%20physical%20photo%20book.%20I%20still%20didn't%20look.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20after%20I%20was%20deeper%20into%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fintuitive-eating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintuitive%20eating%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20about%20six%20months%20later%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I%20finally%20looked%20through%20the%20photo%20book.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20started%20to%20flip%20through%20the%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20beautiful.%20I%20mean%2C%20these%20pictures%20were%20stunning.%20All%20the%20brave%20little%20choices%20I%20made%20came%20together%20in%20peak%20allure.%20I%20had%20found%20beauty%20in%20just%20being%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20when%20people%20come%20to%20our%20home%2C%20I'm%20proud%20to%20point%20them%20to%20the%20wedding%20book%20sitting%20on%20the%20coffee%20table%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-photos-photography-contest-winners-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20photos%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbride-stopped-dieting-before-wedding-day-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720354622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66845f1b268f62ba18a6e4eb%3Fformat%3Djpe