%20when%20the%20accident%20occurred.%20After%20the%20crash%2C%20the%20car's%20number%20plate%20was%20taken%20off%20and%20kept%20inside%20the%20car%20to%20avoid%20identification%20of%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah's%20father%20and%20the%20driver%20are%20being%20questioned%20while%20a%20search%20is%20on%20to%20locate%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720343700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6353of4o_aaditya-thackeray_625x300_07_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-want-to-give-political-colour-aaditya-thackeray-on-mumbai-hit-and-run-6052592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20a%20speeding%20BMW%20hit%20a%20man%20and%20his%20wife%20in%20Mumbai's%20Worli%2C%20killing%20the%20woman%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20said%20he%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20add%20any%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20colour%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-want-to-give-political-colour-aaditya-thackeray-on-mumbai-hit-and-run-6052592%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-want-to-give-political-colour-aaditya-thackeray-on-mumbai-hit-and-run-6052592%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-want-to-give-political-colour-aaditya-thackeray-on-mumbai-hit-and-run-6052592%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jay%20Shah%20Ends%20ODI%2C%20Test%20Captaincy%20Debate%20With%20Big%20Rohit%20Sharma%20Announcement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20on%20Sunday%20congratulated%20Team%20India%20for%20winning%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20in%20West%20Indies%20via%20a%20video%20message%20and%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20winning%20next%20year's%20World%20Test%20Championship%20Final%20and%20Champions%20Trophy%20under%20Rohit%20Sh