xz8Y%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1809851004181258427%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20secretary%20outlined%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20final%20five%20overs%20of%20the%20summit%20clash%20that%20shifted%20momentum%20towards%20India%20as%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20bagged%20crucial%20wickets%20while%20Suryakumar%20Yadav's%20flying%20catch%20on%20the%20boundary%20rope%20put%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20to%20make%20India%20triumphant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20five%20overs%20in%20the%20final%20made%20a%20big%20contribution%20to%20this%20victory.%20For%20this%20contribution%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20extend%20my%20utmost%20thank%20to%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20(Jasprit)%20Bumrah%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20he%20put%20faith%20in%20Rohit's%20leadership%20to%20win%20their%20first%20WTC%20Final%20and%20Champions%20Trophy%20too%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20this%20victory%2C%20the%20next%20stage%20is%20the%202025%20WTC%20final%20and%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20I%20am%20truly%20confident%20that%20we%20will%20win%20both%20the%20tournaments%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20Once%20again%2C%20thank%20you%20all.%20Jai%20Hind%2C%20Jai%20Bharat%2C%20Vande%20Mataram%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20team%20returned%20on%20Thursday%20and%20was%20hosted%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20before%20leaving%20for%20Mumbai%20for%20a%20victory%20parade%20from%20Nariman%20Point%20to%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%20The%20team%20received%20a%20125%20crore%20prize%20money%20from%20BCCI%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20bringing%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20back%20on%20home%20soil%20after