lections.%20The%20index%20has%20surpassed%20year-end%20targets%20set%20by%20numerous%20brokerage%20firms.%20Leading%20investors%20project%20the%20Sensex%20to%20potentially%20reach%20the%201%20lakh%20mark%20within%20the%20next%20three%20to%20five%20years.%20Billionaire%20investor%20Mark%20Mobius%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20India's%20bullish%20market%2C%20suggesting%20the%20Sensex%20could%20even%20breach%201%20lakh%20before%20the%20end%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sensex%20jumped%20from%2070%2C000%20to%2080%2C000%20in%20less%20than%20seven%20months.%20Since%20its%20inception%20at%20100%20in%20April%201979%2C%20it%20has%20grown%20by%20an%20impressive%2015.9%25%20annually%2C%20expanding%20800-fold.%20Doubling%20from%201%2C000%20to%202%2C000%20points%20took%201.48%20years%2C%20and%20further%20to%204%2C000%20points%20in%20just%200.21%20years%20by%20March%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20took%206.33%20years%20to%20double%20from%205%2C000%20to%2010%2C000%20points%20in%20February%202006.%20Subsequently%2C%20it%20doubled%20again%20to%2020%2C000%20points%20in%201.84%20years%2C%20and%20to%2040%2C000%20points%20in%2011.45%20years%20by%20May%202019.%20From%2040%2C000%20to%2080%2C000%2C%20the%20journey%20spanned%20five%20years%20and%201.5%20months.%20On%20an%20average%2C%20the%20benchmark%20index%20doubled%20in%20a%20little%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fs69o6ku8_sensex-1_625x300_07_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20historical%20CAGR%20of%2016%25%2C%20achieving%20the%201%20lakh%20milestone%20by%20December%202025%20seems%20optimistic%20yet%20feasible%2C%20if%20sustained%20growth%20continues.%20However%2C%20maintaining%20such%20high%20returns%20from%20a%20higher%20base%20could%20prove%20challenging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Sensex%20more%20than%20tripling%20since%20its%20March%202020%20lows%2C%20optimism%20remains%20tempered%20by%20potential%20market%20volatility%20ahead.%20Along%20the%20path%20to%201%20lakh%2C%20three%20key%20indicators%20emerge%20as%20crucial%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnHistorical%20Doubling%20Periods%3A%20While%20past%20performance%20isn't%20indicative%20of%20future%20outcomes%2C%20Sensex's%20quickest%20doubling%20-%20from%202%2C000%20to%204%2C000%20points%20-%20took%20just%202.5%20months%20in%201992.%20Conversely%2C%20its%20longest%20doubling%20period%20was%20from%202007%20to%202019%2C%20taking%20about%2011.5%20years%20to%20jump%20from%2020%2C000%20to%2040%2C000%20points.%20The%20index%20reached%2050%2C000%20points%20in%20January%202021%2C%20suggesting%20a%20historical%20doubling%20period%20of%20approximately%20five%20years%2C%20potentially%20placing%201%20lakh%20within%20reach%20by%20January%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESensex%20Returns%20And%20GDP%20Growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20nominal%20terms%20(before%20adjusting%20for%20inflation)%2C%20Sensex%20has%20delivered%20a%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20close%20to%2016%25%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201979%2C%20over%20the%20past%2045%20years.%20This%20growth%20rate%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20nominal%20GDP%20growth%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%20is%20projected%20to%20grow%20at%206.5%25-7%25%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20as%20India%20becomes%20the%20third-largest%20economy.%20Assuming%20a%20nominal%20return%20of%207%25%20annually%20for%20the%20next%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20the%20Sensex%20could%20reach%20a%20value%20of%20around%201%20lakh%20by%20December%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMarket%20Cap%20to%20GDP%20Ratio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%202024%2C%20the%20market%20cap%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20stood%20at%20135%25.%20Over%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20the%20average%20ratio%20has%20been%20above%2083%25%2C%20suggesting%20that%20current%20market%20valuations%20may%20be%20relatively%20high%20compared%20to%20the%2020-year%20historical%20average.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20hit%20a%20bottom%20around%20the%20same%20ratio%20in%202020%20following%20COVID-19%2C%20as%20it%20did%20in%20March%202009%20after%20the%20Global%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%20at%2053%25-55%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplications%20Of%20A%20Market%20Correction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20analysts%20believe%20the%20markets%20are%20overheated%2C%20citing%20the%20high%20market%20cap%20to%20GDP%20ratio%2C%20and%20anticipate%20an%20imminent%20correction.%20The%20exact%20timing%20and%20extent%20of%20this%20correction%20are%20difficult%20to%20predict%20accurately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20a%20correction%20of%2010%25%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20achieving%20an%20annual%20return%20of%2012%25%20would%20be%20necessary%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20of%201%20lakh%20by%202027.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20a%2020%25%20correction%2C%20a%20return%20of%2016%25%20per%20year%20would%20be%20required.%20Both%2012%25%20and%2016%25%20annual%20returns%20are%20considered%20ambitious%20given%20the%20large%20base%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20correction%20of%2010%25-20%25%20occurs%2C%20the%201%20lakh%20milestone%20might%20be%20achieved%20by%202029%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20conclusion%20of%20Modi's%20third%20term.%20However%2C%20if%20no%20correction%20occurs%2C%20Sensex%20appears%20to%20be%20on%20track%20to%20reach%20the%20target%20by%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20o