ud%20Indian%20citizen%20and%20till%20my%20last%20breath%20I%20will%20remain%20so%20but%20I%20have%20one%20common%20fact%20with%20Joe%20Biden%20.%20Both%20of%20us%20have%20exactly%20equal%20chance%20of%20becoming%20the%20next%20president%20of%20USA%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Javed%20Akhtar%20(%40Javedakhtarjadu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJavedakhtarjadu%2Fstatus%2F1809469614847402435%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20proud%20Indian%20citizen%20and%20till%20my%20last%20breath%20I%20will%20remain%20so%20but%20I%20have%20one%20common%20fact%20with%20Joe%20Biden.%20Both%20of%20us%20have%20exactly%20equal%20chance%20of%20becoming%20the%20next%20president%20of%20USA%20(sic)%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Akhtar%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20media%20user%20had%20commented%20on%20the%20industry%20veteran's%20post%20and%20called%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20son%20of%20%3Cem%3EGaddar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewho%20divided%20our%20nation%26quot%3B%20on%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Akhtar%2C%20known%20for%20his%20vocal%20views%20on%20a%20range%20of%20topics%2C%20clapped%20back%20at%20the%20user%20on%20Saturday%20and%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20decide%20whether%20you%20are%20totally%20ignorant%20or%20a%20complete%20idiot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%201857%20my%20family%20has%20been%20involved%20with%20freedom%20movement%20n%20has%20gone%20to%20jails%20and%20Kala%20paani%20when%20most%20probably%20your%20baap%20dadas%20were%20licking%20the%20boots%20of%20Angrez%20sarkar%20(sic).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2079-year-old%20writer%20is%20the%20son%20of%20lyricist-poet%20Jan%20Nisar%20Akhtar%2C%20who%20was%20an%20active%20part%20of%20the%20Progressive%20Writers'%20Movement%20in%20pre-Partition%20British%20India%2C%20and%20writer%20Safiya%20Siraj-ul%20Haq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20great%20great%20grandfather%20Fazl-e-Haq%20K