e%20body%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20photographs%20shared%20with%20them%2C%20and%20later%20physically%20verified%20it%20at%20the%20GMCH%20morgue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinash%20Sarkar%20had%20slipped%20from%20his%20father's%20scooter%20and%20fell%20into%20the%20open%20drain%20on%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20as%20they%20were%20returning%20home%20amid%20a%20heavy%20downpour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20agencies%2C%20including%20NDRF%20and%20SDRF%2C%20had%20launched%20a%20search%20operation%2C%20pressing%20into%20action%20different%20machinery%20and%20sniffer%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinash's%20father%20had%20also%20carried%20out%20a%20search%20operation%20by%20himself%2C%20wading%20through%20the%20drain%2C%20slush%20and%20garbage%20with%20a%20stick%20in%20his%20hand%20for%20the%20last%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20had%20visited%20the%20search%20site%20on%20Saturday%2C%20and%20consoled%20the%20family%2C%20assuring%20all%20measures%20to%20find%20the%20missing%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20condoled%20the%20death%20of%20the%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHCM%20Dr%20%40himantabiswa%20has%20expressed%20his%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20Shri%20Hiralal%20Sarkar%20and%20family%20on%20their%20tragic%20loss.%20HCM%20also%20thanked%20the%20NDRF%2C%20SDRF%2C%20Assam%20Police%20and%20District%20authorities%20for%20their%20search%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CMO%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720334340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F3gt44o6_hiralal-sarkar-himanta_625x300_07_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fguwahati-rains-body-of-8-year-old-who-fell-in-a-drain-found-after-3-day-long-search-op-6052081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20body%20of