d-as-irans-new-president-13173966%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20To%20Start%20Indoor%20Saffron%20Farming%3F%2022-YO%20Earning%20in%20Lakhs%20Shares%20Step-by-Step%20Guide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Patil%E2%80%99s%20family%20cultivates%20bananas%2C%20watermelon%2C%20and%20cotton%20on%20120%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Nandurbar%20village%20in%20Maharashtra.%20However%2C%20productivity%20has%20been%20decreasing%20owing%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20extreme%20weather%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20December%202022%20when%20our%20cotton%20crop%20was%20being%20harvested%2C%20it%20suddenly%20started%20raining.%20Due%20to%20these%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20we%20suffer%20huge%20losses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20his%20worried%20father%2C%20Harsh%20wanted%20to%20explore%20novel%20technologies%20and%20methods%20of%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20do%20jobs%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20I%20was%20more%20inclined%20to%20do%20business%20as%20jobs%20in%20the%20tech%20field%20are%20at%20constant%20threat%20of%20recession%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20year%20of%20his%20college%2C%20Harsh%20started%20looking%20for%20business%20opportunities%20across%20various%20industries.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20my%20parents%20were%20against%20this%20idea.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20focus%20completely%20on%20my%20studies%20first.%20I%20did%20not%20quit%20on%20that%20idea%20but%20instead%20started%20exploring%20business%20opportunities%20in%20agriculture%20so%20that%20my%20parents%20understand%20the%20work%20and%20did%20not%20object%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20pursuing%20his%20higher%20education%20in%20computer%20science%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20Harsh%20started%20looking%20for%20new%20technologies%20and%20methods%20of%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20researching%2C%20I%20came%20across%20new%20crops%20like%20dragon%20fruits%2C%20sandalwood%2C