.com%2F354559%2Fdoctors-day-orthopaedic-surgeon-inspiring-story-dr-sakshi-maheshwari-accident-broken-bones-civil-hospital-ahmedabad%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20an%20MBA%20Grad%20Made%20Her%20Family%20Farm%20Profitable%20With%20Vegetables%3B%20Earns%20Rs%201.5%20Crore%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20says%20that%20farming%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20profitable%3F%20People%20generally%20have%20a%20notion%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20small%20and%20not%20viable.%20Nothing%20can%20be%20farther%20from%20the%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smarika%20Chandrakar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enterprising%20MBA%20graduate%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348905%2Fhydroponics-training-workshop-in-gujarat-india-rasik-nakum-one-farm-hydroponics-rajkot-teaching-soil-less-water-less-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarming%20family%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Charmudiya%20village%20in%20Chattisgarh.%20Her%20childhood%20was%20spent%20in%20the%20lush%20green%20paddy%20fields%20with%20her%20father%20and%20grandfather%20where%20she%20learnt%20her%20first%20lessons%20about%20life%20and%20farming.%20Like%20any%20other%20business%2C%20they%20had%20good%20and%20bad%20times%20as%20well%20which%20the%20young%20girl%20was%20quick%20to%20adapt%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20choosing%20a%20career%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20pursue%20an%20engineering%20degree%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%20Raipur%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20MBA%20from%20Pune.%20After%20working%20as%20a%20senior%20business%20development%20executive%20for%20over%20five%20years%20in%20Pune%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Raipur%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20allowed%20her%20to%20spend%20weekends%20at%20home%2C%20which%20were%20invariably%20at%20the%20farm.%20She%20started%20learning%20the%20finer%20nuances%20of%20p