t%20oil%20is%20considered%20the%20mother%20of%20all%20oils%20owing%20to%20its%20health%20benefits.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20goodness%20in%20it.%20It%20also%20acts%20as%20an%20immunity%20booster%20and%20is%20the%20best%20moisturiser.%20Mothers%20can%20even%20apply%20the%20oil%20on%20newborn%20babies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sumila%20believes%20launching%20her%20own%20company%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20her.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESumila%20believes%20launching%20her%20own%20company%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20her.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20testimonials.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20a%20doctor%20who%20was%20using%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%20to%20treat%20ulcers%20in%20children%20who%20were%20cancer%20patients.%20Usually%2C%20children%20develop%20painful%20ulcers%20in%20their%20mouth%20post%20chemotherapy.%20This%20testimonial%20really%20surprised%20me%20and%20also%20ignited%20the%20passion%20insi